<section sectnbr = "1F">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "06">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A1606014" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Radiator Removal and Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A1606013">Radiator On-Vehicle Inspection and Cleaning</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A1606014001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove radiator cooling fan assembly. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1606011"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
For CVT model, drain CVT fluid. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A5506003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove front bumper. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9806003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
With pipe connected, detach A/C condenser assembly from radiator. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A7206006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
The A/C condenser assembly may be damaged if it hits against or interferes with other parts.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Suspend the removed A/C condenser assembly in a place where no damaged will be caused during removal and installation of the radiator.
</ptxt>
</attention4>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove radiator outlet hose from radiator.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
For CVT model, disconnect CVT fluid cooler inlet and outlet hoses from radiator.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove radiator upper brackets (1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove radiator (2) from vehicle.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70P160007.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "62.569mm" ver = "01" gw = "193" gh = "161"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A1606014002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
Reverse removal procedure noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
If there is matchmark on each of hose and pipe, install the hose aligning matchmark on hose with matchmark on pipe and then install each clamp in proper position.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Refill cooling system with coolant. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1606005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
For CVT model, refill CVT with specified fluid. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A5506003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check cooling system for leakage. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1606003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
For CVT model, check for CVT fluid leakage.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
